      "raw_text": "A bridge on the Northern Pacific\neast of Hope, Idaho. was washed out\nsome time last night and all trains\nfrom the east are marked indefinite\"\nSome trains are IL hours late.\n\n\n1t will take \"a hours to repair the\ndamage temporarily and in the mean\ntime passengers will be transferred\nat the point OF the washout. Trains\nwere made up in Spokane to bring in\nthe passengers of trains held up by\nthe washout."
